This map is completely scratch made and terrain and build style is more or less like de_dust2, I know you will like this map

Features:
24 Spawn Points
Bombsites A and B
Bot Navigation file included (tested and working)
Cubemaps done and working
Alleys and ramps
Environment terrain outside map to make it look realistic and in flow with the world

If there is something that should be changed, please comment.
If you like this map, please do not forget to rate

I will add updates to this map accordingly.

If you want to build it further or for CS:GO, you can do it without any prior permission, just credit me is all I ask :)

Thanks
